Dan Orban - CSCI 5607 - Assignment 0

This program takes an imput file with "imsize width height" as its first line 
and outputs a PPM file of width and height with a pattern.

Build the program with make.

Program usage:
    ray_tracer <input.txt> <output.ppm>

Example input file:
	# Eye position
	eye  0.0 0.0 5.0
	# 
	viewdir  0.0 0.0 -1.0
	updir  0.0 1.0 0.0
	fovh  90.0
	imsize  500 500

	bkgcolor 0.0 0.0 0.0

	mtlcolor  1.0 0.0 0.0
	sphere  0.0 0.0 -10.0 4.0
	mtlcolor  0.0 1.0 0.0
	sphere  0.5 0.0 -5.0 1.0
	sphere  -0.5 3.0 -5.0 1.0